image_analysis.description: A photograph of a high-end bathroom interior. The room features white marble flooring and wall tiling. A white vanity with a marble countertop holds various toiletries, a black soap dispenser, and a black container. Above the vanity is a large mirror reflecting the opposite side of the room. To the left, an open doorway leads to a separate toilet area. A white towel hangs on a chrome rack on the left wall. A black trash can sits on the floor near the vanity, and a white bath mat is placed in front of the cabinets.
image_analysis.layout: Interior architectural photograph showing a bathroom and an adjacent toilet room through an open door.
